<!-- ==========================================================
     Project: WpfHexEditor.Shell
     File: HighContrast/Colors.xaml
     Author: Derek Tremblay (derektremblay666@gmail.com)
     Contributors: Claude (Anthropic)
     Created: 2026-03-19
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the High Contrast theme. Pure black
         (#000000) background with maximum-contrast white (#FFFFFF) text and
         WCAG AAA accessibility accents: bright yellow (#FFFF00) for focus/
         active, cyan (#1AEBFF) for selection, bright green (#3FF23F) for
         disabled states. Designed for users with visual impairments.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in HighContrastTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Dark/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

